</p>
<p style=\"text-align:center;\">
	<span style=\"font-family:monospace;font-size:medium;\"><img src=\"/Public/kindupload/image/20180806/20180806143234_79807.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p style=\"text-align:center;\">
	<span style=\"font-family:monospace;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:monospace;font-size:medium;\">(上图为</span><span style=\"font-family:monospace;font-size:medium;\">丹尼尔·</span><span style=\"font-family:monospace;font-size:medium;\">波特</span><span style=\"font-family:monospace;font-size:medium;\">及护士团队</span><span style=\"font-family:monospace;font-size:medium;\">)</span></span> 
