</p>
<p style=\"text-align:center;\">
	<embed id=\"player\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" src=\"/Public/kindupload/media/20180814/20180814100301_53525.mp4\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"550\" height=\"400\" autostart=\"false\" loop=\"true\" />
</p>
<p style=\"text-align:center;\">
